{"tid":654173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大 校長 錢大康：堅持用廣東話教學　收不到大陸學生　不是國際化了","createTime":"2018-05-05T11:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T07:51:51.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":156,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"ee477b082489cb0642b6c7b2670de6fe67e436c8","tid":654173,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:41:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkbumountaingod/photos/a.1569446790012488.1073741828.1569129996710834/1892990104324820/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkbumountaingod%2Fphotos%2Fa.1569446790012488.1073741828.1569129996710834%2F1892990104324820%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=Z0k%2FYHbF8MaaLJQ2u3fBcbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=6b06b6f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkbumountaingod/photos/a.1569446790012488.1073741828.1569129996710834/1892990104324820/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n錢大康之野心何止推普？自普通話畢業門檻抗議事件後，錢大康鮮有接受傳媒專訪，但就喺信報唯一一篇專訪，揚言大學不可以堅持粵語教學。<br />\n<br />\n佢話：「大環境變了，大學也得跟着變，比如教學語言，如果只堅持用廣東話教學，那可能就收不到大陸學生（除了會粵語的），學校就不是國際化了。每一任校長都不能一成不變，由A變B，最緊要知道B是什麼，才能向前邁進。」<br />\n<br />\n咁點解「收大陸學生」就係「國際化」？除非你信錢大康撐香港獨立，否則即係亂噏一通，話知你死，總知我大晒。<br />\n<br />\n一年之前，錢大康想改動浸大教學語言，借山神搞撤普公投後搞「大學語文政策檢討」，諗住大幅減少粵語教學。幸有陳士齊老師挺身而出，同山神聯合收集逾五百簽名，準備發動公投，校方先派出高層談判，承諾唔會改變既有課堂語言，咁先作罷。<br />\n<br />\n估唔到校方出爾反爾，一年之後更加猖狂，先有陰死七成豁免試學生，再將同學停學。如今睇錢大康最新訪談，就知「普通話檢討」根本就係廢，浸大只會變本加厲，師生嘅苦難陸續有嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/hPZnxf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FhPZnxf&h=660eaab1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a894d43e6883dae0be223884c7cd8ed9216ca68","tid":654173,"uid":123711,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:43:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7a0848d81e531bebbb769962034d97d8c462925","tid":654173,"uid":2507,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:44:38.000Z","msg":"佢咁講算唔算變相港獨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大陸學生＝國際化？"},{"pid":"aa4ce099ec052e6cc35a9c01eeec86abecf6c47b","tid":654173,"uid":52068,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"9a894d43e6883dae0be223884c7cd8ed9216ca68","tid":654173,"uid":123711,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:43:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:45:07.000Z","msg":"全世界也是中國的"},{"pid":"b74d4f4c96cfdb8a95d8d0917299274b7c900f54","tid":654173,"uid":123711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:45:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94d162f8012645204ad33e048fa56470a67ba89b","tid":654173,"uid":3873,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:46:06.000Z","msg":"你睇吓有幾多贏國學生喺美國讀書，再睇吓有冇邊間美國大學因爲收多咗贏國學生而改用普通話教書"},{"pid":"a705b4fd0096b4c9a648bcb9c6a36b417db21b1d","tid":654173,"uid":19072,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:53:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"824b3ff2147daa6f39c3b74168fad17fd7665319","tid":654173,"uid":117837,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:57:43.000Z","msg":"錢大康我屌你老母.jpg"},{"pid":"4d4e4546d31be334c9c31320d4a058f3e460a67e","tid":654173,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T12:00:38.000Z","msg":"英國美國d學校國唔國際化？"},{"pid":"50eb7a85dd9271069ca3cf2c07835ec9d1e62f63","tid":654173,"uid":117837,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/223044_5b3b7545a62a4635223f2bc0de3c2e79.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F223044_5b3b7545a62a4635223f2bc0de3c2e79.jpeg&h=25e7705d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f007e24d894488d49f59736c692fec94528ffdf","tid":654173,"uid":27038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T12:11:56.000Z","msg":"屌你唔用全英文！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi